Parameters:
fade - whether the particles have to fade out or not
smoke - whether you want smoke particles or dot particles
amount - the amount of particles
inner - the radius of the inner core
outer - the radius of the outer core
smokeRadius - the radius of the smoke particles for the gaussian filter
